@startuml UC-006: View Submission Results

title UC-006: View Submission Results
autonumber

actor User
participant "Client" as Client
participant "Submission API" as API
participant "SubmissionService" as SubmissionService
database "MongoDB" as DB

== View Single Submission (Student) ==
User -> Client: Click on submission
Client -> API: GET /v0/submissions/:jobId

API -> API: Verify authentication (JWT)

API -> SubmissionService: getSubmissionByJobId(jobId)
SubmissionService -> DB: findOne({jobId})

alt Submission found
    DB --> SubmissionService: Submission with grading results
    SubmissionService --> API: Complete submission data
    API --> Client: 200 OK + full results
    Client -> Client: Parse test results and group results
    Client --> User: Display results:\n- Total points earned/possible\n- Per-test results with status\n- Group results (if grouped)\n- Execution time
else Submission not found
    DB --> SubmissionService: null
    SubmissionService --> API: Not found
    API --> Client: 404 Not Found
    Client --> User: Submission not found
end

== View Student's Submission History ==
User -> Client: View "My Submissions"
Client -> API: GET /v0/submissions/student/:studentId

API -> API: Verify user is student or instructor

API -> SubmissionService: getSubmissionsByStudent(studentId, filters)
SubmissionService -> DB: find({studentId, ...filters}).sort({createdAt: -1})
DB --> SubmissionService: List of submissions
SubmissionService --> API: Submissions array
API --> Client: 200 OK + submissions list
Client --> User: Display submission history:\n- Lab name\n- Status (pending/running/completed)\n- Points earned\n- Submission date

== View Lab Overview (Instructor) ==
User -> Client: View lab submissions dashboard
Client -> API: GET /v0/submissions/lab/:labId

API -> API: Verify instructor role

API -> SubmissionService: getLabSubmissionOverview(labId)
SubmissionService -> DB: Aggregate submissions by student
DB --> SubmissionService: Lightweight overview per student
SubmissionService --> API: Overview data
API --> Client: 200 OK + lab overview
Client --> User: Display class overview:\n- Student progress\n- Latest submission per student\n- Completion statistics\n- Average scores

@enduml
